-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>After that hike, relax at the natural hot springs of La Fortuna that are heated to a comfortable 35-38 degrees by the Volcano Arenal. Most of these springs are owned by hotels, so you have to pay for a day pass or stay at the hotel to access them. We highly recommend <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tabacon-cr\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Tabacon Hot Springs.<\/a> However, there is also a free and public hot spring for you to visit.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Did you know: <\/strong>Costa Rica has over 30 protected national parks!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25182453\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-1.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica 7 day travel guide arenal volcano\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"costa rica 7 day travel guide arenal volcano\" class=\"wp-image-77030 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25182453\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25182453\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25182453\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.co