all from an incredible height of 45 meters (148 feet)!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/la-fortuna\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best Things To Do in La Fortuna<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25184424\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-7.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica 7 day travel guide hanging bridges monteverde\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"costa rica 7 day travel guide hanging bridges monteverde\" class=\"wp-image-77045 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25184424\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-7.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25184424\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-7-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25184424\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-7-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25184424\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-7-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25184424\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-7-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25184424\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-7-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25184424