here-to-stay-in-monteverde\">Where to Stay in Monteverde<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Monteverde offers numerous accommodation options, from cabins in the forest to hotels in Santa Elena. (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/monteverde-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See all your hotels options here<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><div class=\"products__container\">\n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/los-pinos-lodge-monteverde\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03224856\/chira-glamping-monteverde-30x20.jpeg\" alt=\"Los Pinos Lodge\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03224856\/chira-glamping-monteverde-450x300.jpeg\">\n                    <div class=\"product__content\">\n                        <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                        <div class=\"product__content-title\">Los Pinos Lodge<\/div>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/chira-glamping-monteverde\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03224905\/los-pinos-lodge-30x20.jpeg\" alt=\"Chira Glamping\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03224905\/los