ld&#x2019;s most beautiful national parks: Manuel Antonio National Park. Here you can spot a vast array of wildlife!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you arrive in Manuel Antonio around midday, either relax at the beach, Playa Espadilla Norte, or opt for a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/manuel-coffee-choco-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Chocolate &amp; Coffee tour<\/a>.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Get to know <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">everything about Manuel Antonio<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190346\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-13.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica 7 day travel guide manuel antonio beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"costa rica 7 day travel guide manuel antonio beach\" class=\"wp-image-77058 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190346\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-13.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190346\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-13-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190346\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-13-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190346\/costa-rica-7-da