y-car\"><strong>By car:<\/strong><\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>It is an easy 4-hour drive from Monteverde to Manuel Antonio and the longest drive on this 7-day Costa Rica itinerary. However, all the roads are good, and you will not need a 4&#xD7;4 car. About halfway, make a quick stop at the famous <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/pFnMvmiymcDAsgP5A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Crocodile Bridge<\/a>, where you have a chance of spotting crocodiles. Please do not buy any meat from the sellers because feeding animals is a bad example of wildlife tourism. Besides: <em>you are not allowed to feed animals in Costa Rica by law.&#xA0;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Lunch tip:<\/strong> Grab a quick but tasty lunch at <a href=\"https:\/\/g.page\/eljardinorotina\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">El Jardin<\/a>, about halfway through your drive. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27174205\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-21.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-77177 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27174205\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-21.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27174205\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-21-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27174205\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-21-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27174205\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-21-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27174205\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-21-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27174205\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-21-163x109.jpg 163w, https