ternatively, book a direct shuttle between both destinations.&#xA0;(<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transport-monteverde-manuelantonio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See the shuttle options here<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190430\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-15.jpg\" alt=\"manuel anotino beach costa rica guide\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"manuel anotino beach costa rica guide\" class=\"wp-image-77062 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190430\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-15.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190430\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-15-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190430\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-15-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190430\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-15-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190430\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-15-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190430\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-15-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190430\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-15-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190430\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-15-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190430\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-15-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190430\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-15-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190430\/c