rcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27230700\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-33.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-where-to-stay-in-manuel-antonio\">Where to Stay in Manuel Antonio<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The closer your accommodation is to Manuel Antonio National Park, the more expensive it gets. Therefore, we recommend staying between Quepos and the national park if you have your own transport.&#xA0;(<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/manuel-antonio-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See all your hotel options here<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><div class=\"products__container\">\n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/the-falls-manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/15000631\/the-falls-30x20.jpeg\" alt=\"The Falls Hotel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/15000631\/the-falls-450x300.jpeg\">\n                    <div class=\"product__content\">\n                        <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                        <div class=\"product__content-title\">The Falls Hotel<\/div>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a clas