   <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/flights-to-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Find the best flights to Costa Rica here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p>You can also cross borders from Panama or Nicaragua if you&#x2019;re already in one of these countries.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-getting-around-costa-rica\">Getting Around Costa Rica<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-by-car\">By Car<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The easiest way, by far, to get around Costa Rica is with a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">rental car<\/a>. In addition, you get the freedom to stop anywhere you like, at your own pace, which gives you the flexibility to complete your 7-day itinerary in Costa Rica. It&#x2019;s good to know that rental car prices double in the high season.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27174149\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-20.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica 7 day travel guide volcano\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"323\" alt=\"costa rica 7 day travel guide volcano\" class=\"wp-image-77175 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27174149\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-20.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27174149\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-20-800x575.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27174149\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-20-1080x776.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27174149\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-20-450x323.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.s