nk\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">La Fortuna<\/a> to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/monteverde\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Monteverde<\/a>. Because of this, always use the Waze app in Costa Rica to find the right roads. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Parking locals may walk up to you and ask for a very small payment to watch your car. This is a good service in general except when they try to overcharge you.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h5 id=\"do-i-need-a-4x4-in-costa-rica\"><strong>Do I need a 4&#xD7;4 in Costa Rica?<\/strong><\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>You no longer need a 4&#xD7;4 car to get to Costa Rica if you follow the main roads. However, to avoid any pothole damage, we recommend renting a car with some clearance from the ground.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>If you&#x2019;re planning to rent a car in Costa Rica, we recommend using <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a> because all insurances needed are included in the price <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">displayed on their website<\/a>. No hidden costs.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25190449\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-16.j