te Hostel<\/a><\/li><li>La Fortuna: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/lafortuna-casaluna\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Casa Luna<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/lafortuna-sangregado\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sangregado Lodge<\/a>, and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/la-fortuna-poshpacker-hostel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Poshpacker Hostel<\/a><\/li><li>Monteverde: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/los-pinos-lodge-monteverde\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Los Pinos Lodge<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/chira-glamping-monteverde\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Chira Glamping<\/a>, and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/monteverde-outbox-inn-hostel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Outbox Hostel<\/a><\/li><li>Manuel Antonio: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/the-falls-manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">The Falls Hotel<\/a>, and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/teva-manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Teva Hostel<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"budget\">How Much Does 7 days in Costa Rica Cost?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Costa Rica contains 5% of the world&#x2019;s biodiversity, being one of the world&#x2019;s biodiverse countries. But it is also known as &#x2018;Switzerland of Central America&#x2019; because of the high prices that come with the country&#x2019;s beauty.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"expenses-for-a-7-day-costa-rica-itinerary\">Expenses for a 7-day Costa Rica Itinerary<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>An itinerary of 7 days in Costa Rica will cost you anywhere between 1400 &#x2013; 2400 USD. For example, this includes going out for lunch and dinner, accommodation, entrances to attractions, and a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">rental car<\/a>. If you travel with two or more, you&#x2019;ll split your rental car and accommodation costs.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-budget\">\n        <span class=\"block-budget__title\">Budget<\/span><ul class=\"block-budget__list\"><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Hotel: 50-150 USD \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Hostel: 10-180 USD \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--restaurants\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Price per meal: 15 &#x2013; 30 USD \n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Entrances: 125 &#x2013; 250 USD \/ week\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Transport: 600 &#x2013; 1000 USD \/ week\n                    <\/li><\/ul><\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27231007\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-29.jpg\" alt=\"food costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"238\" height=\"338\" alt=\"food costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-77219 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1353px) 100vw, 1353px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27231007\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-29.jpg 1353w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27231007\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-29-423x600.jpg 423w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27231007\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-29-571x810.jpg 571w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27231007\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-29-238x338.jpg 238w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27231007\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-29-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27231007\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-29-115x163.jpg 115w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27231007\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-29-127x180.jpg 127w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27231007\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-29-541x768.jpg 541w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27231007\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-29-722x1024.jpg 722w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27231007\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-29-761