est sim card providers in the country are Movistar, Claro and Kolbi. In our experience, Movistar has the most solid connection throughout the country. Costs for this are 10.000 Colones for 5GB. (&#xB1; 15 USD)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Budget tip!<\/strong>&#xA0;The currency in Costa Rica is Colones. Save on exchange fees by converting your own local currency to Colones with a&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transferwise\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Wise card<\/a>. You can use that card to withdraw Colones from the ATM in Costa Rica or pay by card at pretty much all the shops. Some restaurants charge USD by default, but it will significantly affect the total bill if you ask them to charge Colones.&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transferwise\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Get a Wise card here; it&#x2019;s free!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/28154512\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-37-1080x744.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica 7 day travel itinerary horse riding\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"310\" alt=\"costa rica 7 day travel itinerary horse riding\" class=\"wp-image-77261 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/28154512\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-37-1080x744.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/28154512\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-37-800x551.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/28154512\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-37-450x310.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/28154512\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-37-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/28154512\/costa-rica-7-day-guide